first.scala : Simple Scala program illustrating the use of singleton class
  
lambda.scala : Simple Scala program illustrating anonymous functions (lambda's)

functionsubtyping.scala : Scala program illustrating function subtyping
    
second.scala : Scala program illustrating derivation and subtyping
    
pattern.scala : Scala program illustrating case classes and pattern matching
    
tree.scala : Scala program illustrating bounded generic type parameters.
    
variant.scala : Scala program illustrating covariant subtyping and bounded generic type parameter
    
contravariance.scala : Scala program illustrating contravariant subtyping on generics. 
